4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
5 commemorate the one hundredth anniversary of the Louisiana Municipal Association; does
6 hereby recognize a century of service, progress, community leadership, and a unified voice
7 for local government; and does hereby express enduring appreciation for its continuing
8 mission of education, training, and advocacy.
